mr. airavata is a 2015 indian action-thriller kannada film directed & written by a. p. arjun and produced by sandesh nagaraj . the film stars darshan , urvashi rautela and prakash raj in the lead roles and also stars darshan 's son vineesh making his acting debut . the music is composed by v. harikrishna . the film was released to 450 screens worldwide with 45 screens in the united states , 5 in australia , and in 50 screens outside karnataka and 350 screens in the state .